itk-smoothingrecursiveyvvgaussianfilter provides a GPU (OpenCL) and CPU implementation of the computationally efficient forward and backward IIR Young & Van Vliet recursive Gaussian smoothing filter.
Please refer to:
Vidal-Migallon I., Commowick O., Pennec X., Dauguet J., Vercauteren T.,"GPU and CPU implementation of Young - Van Vliet's Recursive Gaussian Smoothing Filter", Insight Journal, January-December 2013, http://hdl.handle.net/10380/3425.

